Title : Template:ITF wheelchair profile/doc
Text : {{Documentation subpage}}
<!-- Categories go at the bottom of this page and interwikis go in Wikidata. -->
{{Template shortcut|ITF wheelchair}}
{{Uses Wikidata|P4299}}
{{Lua|Module:EditAtWikidata}}

'''{{NAMESPACE}}:{{BASEPAGENAME}}''' displays an external link to a [[wheelchair tennis]] player's profile at [https://www.itftennis.com/ ITFtennis.com], the official website of the [[International Tennis Federation]] (ITF). It is intended for use in the [[Wikipedia:External links|external links]] section of an article.

== Usage ==
Unnamed parameters:
: {{tlcw|{{BASEPAGENAME}} | <var>ID</var> }}
: {{tlcw|{{BASEPAGENAME}} | <var>ID</var> | <var>NAME</var> }}

Named parameters (with "id"):
: {{tlcw|{{BASEPAGENAME}} | id{{=}} <var>ID</var> }}
: {{tlcw|{{BASEPAGENAME}} | id{{=}} <var>ID</var> | name{{=}} <var>NAME</var> }}

Named parameters (with "number"):
: {{tlcw|{{BASEPAGENAME}} | number{{=}} <var>ID</var> }}
: {{tlcw|{{BASEPAGENAME}} | number{{=}} <var>ID</var> | name{{=}} <var>NAME</var> }}

Using [[Wikidata]] property [[d:Property:P4299|P4299]]:
: {{tlcw|{{BASEPAGENAME}} }}
: {{tlcw|{{BASEPAGENAME}} | name{{=}} <var>NAME</var> }}

== Examples ==

=== ID in template ===
''Usage in the article [[Shingo Kunieda]], with article name as link text:''
: {{tlcw|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}} | 100016393 }}
: {{tlcw|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}} | id{{=}} 100016393 }}
: {{tlcw|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}} | number{{=}} 100016393 }}

''Usage with name parameter as link text:''
: {{tlcw|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}} | 100016393 | Shingo Kunieda }}
: {{tlcw|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}} | id{{=}} 100016393 | name{{=}} Shingo Kunieda }}
: {{tlcw|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}} | number{{=}} 100016393 | name{{=}} Shingo Kunieda }}

''Output:''
:* {{{{BASEPAGENAME}} | 100016393 | Shingo Kunieda }}

''URL:''
: <kbd>[https://www.itftennis.com/wheelchair/players/player/profile.aspx?playerid=100016393 https://www.itftennis.com/wheelchair/players/player/profile.aspx?playerid={{hilite|100016393}}]</kbd>

=== ID in Wikidata ===
''Usage in the article [[Esther Vergeer]]:''
: {{tlcw|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}} }}
: {{tlcw|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}} | name{{=}} Esther Vergeer }}

''Output:''
:* {{{{BASEPAGENAME}} | 55000204 | Esther Vergeer }} [[File:Blue pencil.svg |frameless |text-top |10px |alt=Edit this at Wikidata |link=https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q259606#P4299 |Edit this at Wikidata]]

''URL:''
: <kbd>[https://www.itftennis.com/wheelchair/players/player/profile.aspx?playerid=55000204 https://www.itftennis.com/wheelchair/players/player/profile.aspx?playerid={{hilite|55000204}}]</kbd>

=== No ID in template or Wikidata ===
''Usage:''
: {{tlcw|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}} }}

''Output:''
:* {{{{BASEPAGENAME}} }}

